        {
          "character": "player",
          "expression": "normal_01",
          "text": "哦,你会弹钢琴?在练习什么曲子?"
        },
        {
          "character": "Nana",
          "expression": "normal_02",
          "text": "现在在练习肖邦的夜曲...但是很难,还弹不好...",
          "voiceFile": "talk_hobby_002"
        },
        {
          "character": "player",
          "expression": "normal_01",
          "text": "哦...夜曲啊。真厉害。(姑且附和一下)"
        }
      ]
